<div class="title">Retrospective on a Decade of Drinking</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Boozetasm&Exact=1">Boozetasm</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Boozetasm. "Retrospective on a Decade of Drinking: An Experience with Alcohol (exp23442)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 22, 2006. erowid.org/exp/23442</div>

